17. Rg4 Qf6
{ Black has a pair of bishops, and is ready to castle next, while  18.Bg5  can be answered with  18...Bxf3  . In the 2021 correspondence game, players agreed to a draw soon. This position was also reached in the game ½-½ Gelfand, B @@StartBracket@@2703@@EndBracket@@ - Leko, P @@StartBracket@@2690@@EndBracket@@ Batumi 2018. }
