Rxd1 Bxc5 9. Nbd2 c3 10. bxc3 O-O 11. Nb3 Be7
{ Many moves have been tried, at this point, over a period of time. So far mainly  12.c4  and  12.Nfd4  gained popularity. We will see all other lines apart from these two moves here. }
12. Ne1
