{ Black got complete control in the center while White doesn't have any attack on any side of the board. Black threatens to take on c3 and exchange a few more pieces so that White's weak pawn structure becomes more prominent. Black was better in the game 1/2-1/2  Giri,A @@StartBracket@@2764@@EndBracket@@ -Shankland,S @@StartBracket@@2691@@EndBracket@@ chess24.com INT 2021. }
