12. e4 Nxd5 { Getting away from Bg5 ideas. } 13. Bxd5
{ This move is better than Levon's  13.Qxd5  , which he played against Ding in an online tournament in 2021. }
13... O-O 14. b4
{ Trying to create something out of nothing.  14.b3  Qc7  15.Bb2  Na5  would eliminate White's strong bishop on d5, and Black gets a nice play in the queenside. }
14... c4 15. Bb2 Qc7
