10... Nc6 11. h4 { Trying to gain space on the kingside. } 11... h6
{ It is very difficult to suggest how White should continue here. Black's play is simple. They would like to play Qd6-Qb4 or expand on the queenside with a6-b5 or a5-Nb4 etc. }
