11. Rd1
{ Naturally, after seeing the Rc1 variation, the first question that comes to mind is why not do the same with the rook on d1 :@@EndBracket@@ }
11... Bd7
{ Rarely played except one game by a 2317 player. Black targets the rook on d1 and aims to play Ba4 next. }
