{ The deep point of including h6-h3 finally gets clear. Not only is Black out of any back rank issues, but we have also made a target of the pawn on h3. This is the basic introduction of the file. I hope it gives you some impression of what Black wants and what we would like to avoid.  Let us now see the lines. I want everyone to have clarity of the position rather than memorize a bunch of engine-generated moves.   Human understanding and human touch are of utmost importance in any opening. }
