18. Rc1 { White tries to gain a tempo. } 18... Qd6
{ It turns out that Black gains a tempo! Clearly White is not happy to trade rooks, so they would have to waste another move to avoid it. Apart from changing the rooks, Black also has the standard plan of expanding on the queenside with b5-a5-a4. }
