{ Recently this line was also seen in many games. Here White can take the pawn on c4 with either knight. Both  8.Na3  and  8.Nxc4  are equally popular and has been covered in great detail in different chapters. Some novelties had to wait for more than ten years before it was executed and some are still fresh. A separate chapter is entirely devoted to 7.Ne5 . }
