{ After  15.Kxg2  Kxe7  Black king cannot be touched while Black threatens Bc6+. }
15... Kxe7
{ Rook is coming to b8 and the bishop will go to c6. Black has better central control and with an open position, the bishop will be stronger than the knight. }
16. Rfd1
{ White keeps the option of taking the knight with either piece open. } 16...
