10... Rc8 { Not allowing Ne5 } 11. b3
{ Trying to break Black's pawn chain on the queenside. } 11... Be7
{ 11...Na5  has been played a few times, which also gives Black a fine position. Once again, I would like to keep the similar moves as long as it has a similar evaluation. Makes it far easier to understand. }
