{ If we compare this move with  18.Bg5  , we will see this move gives protection to the knight on  f3  that was coming under a double attack with Rd3 at some point. So this move also stops Bg4 ideas just like  18.Bf4  . However, just like  18.Bf4  this move also comes under the same fork from d5 . }
