{ By attacking the knight on a3, Black saves his own knight on a1. } 23. Rxa1
Qxa3 24. Qxd7 Rxc3
{ Every single engine gives 0.00 and in 2018 correspondence game it ended in a draw soon. White is about to lose his pawn on e3 and also his pawn on a2 makes his rook on a1 passive. White's king is also not safe and this fully compensates the material disbalance. ½-½ Ostriker,J @@StartBracket@@2561@@EndBracket@@ -Dothan,Y @@StartBracket@@2538@@EndBracket@@ ICCF email 2018 }
