{ Consolidating the position and stopping Nc2-Bf5 ideas.  14.Kg2  is covered from 13.Kg2 move order. }
14... Bg4 { Developing with tempo is a healthy thing to do :@@EndBracket@@ }
15. Re1 Re8 { Once again buliding more pressure on the pawn. } 16. Ne4 Bb4
{ White is unable to keep the material advantage, and Black keeps the initiative. }
