{ This position occurred in the game Javakhishvili, L @@StartBracket@@2455@@EndBracket@@-Ushenina, A @@StartBracket@@2443@@EndBracket@@ Astana 2019, and here instead of Bg4, which was played in the game, Black had a much stronger move. }
