20. Rdd1
{ Not letting Black activate the rooks, and getting away from Nc4 fork. } 20...
Nc4 21. Bd4 Bc6
{ Black changes the good bishop of White, and the knight on c4 becomes strong. After the trade, Ra8 will be available to put pressure on the a2 pawn. Moves like b5-Nd5 will bring more forces to the queenside. Black had no issues in the game 1/2-1/2  Meier,G @@StartBracket@@2628@@EndBracket@@-Fridman,D @@StartBracket@@2608@@EndBracket@@ Magdeburg 2021 }
