[White "Training Positions"]
[Black "Position #2"]
[Result "*"]

1. d4 Nf6 2. g3 d5 3. Nf3 c5 4. dxc5 e6 5. Bg2 Bxc5 6. O-O Nc6 7. c4 d4 8. a3
a5
{ Black is now ready to O-O and grab the center with e5. Both Bg5 and Ne1-Nd3 plans can be answered with Be7. Black has nothing to complain about from the opening. }
