Nb3 b5 { Making sure White doesn't get Bg2 ideas. } 9. Qxb5 Rb8
{ Attacks the queen, and ready to play Bb7 next. } 10. Qa4 Bb7 11. f3 e4
{ Black opens up the position while White king remains in the center. Soon Qb6 will happen to stop White from castling. Black gets massive compensation for the pawn. }
