19. Bxg5 Qxg5 20. Nd7
{ Thanks to this move, White can temporarily delay resignation. } 20... Nd6 21.
Nxf8 Rxf8
{ Black has two pawns for the exchange, and what pawns! Soon e5-e4 will be coming. The bishop on b7 is a monster. Engines already give -1.45 for Black. }
