16. Rc1 Qb8 { Once again planning to exchange pieces with Rc8. } 17. a5 Rc8
{ Either White will have to allow the trade of rooks or leave the c-file and allow Qc7-Qc3. With outside pawn majority Black should be happy with endgames. }
