19. Nxd2 Nxa2 20. Bxb7
{ It was wiser to play moves like Kf1 and let Black save the pawn when Black is still better but not winning. I am giving this variation, just to demonstrate that White cannot take this pawn and hope to queen the c-pawn. }
20... Rb8 21. Be4 Rb2
{ The engine gives -4 at this point, and it becomes clear upon a closer look that there is no way to deal with straightforward a5-a4 plans. }
