33... Qxf7 34. Nxf7 Nxc1 35. Nd8 { At best Black gets 2 vs 1 which is a draw. }
35... e5 { 35...Ne2  36.Nxe6  Nxg3+  37.Kg2= } 36. Kg2 Kh7 37. Nc6
{ Black loses the e-pawn soon, and the rest does not require any comments. }
