21. Rfc1
{ White's best bet is to play against Black's pieces that lack coordination.  White is unable to take on d5   21.Rxd5  due to  21...Ne3!  Black sacrifices the knight but picks up the rook on f1.  22.fxe3  Bxf1  23.Kxf1  dxe3-+  Soon the rook on h8 will come into the game and that will be the end of White's journey. }
