29... Rc5 30. Rg1
{ The exchange of rooks will free the e1 square for the black knight. } 30...
g5 31. Rd1 Rc3 { White's entire army is getting dominated now. } 32. Kg1 Kf7
33. Kh1 h4 34. Rb1 hxg3 35. hxg3 Nxe3
{ Finally, after improving his position to its maximum Black gives back the knight at the appropriate moment. }
36. fxe3 Rxe3
{ Black is a pawn up, and soon more pawns would drop. Hari had no trouble converting this. }
