32. Bb3 Kd6 33. Kf3 { White forces a draw in the most convincing manner. }
33... Nxd4+ 34. Bxd4 Bxd4 35. h4 e5 36. g4 Kc5 37. Bg8 h6 38. Bf7 g5 39. h5 Kd6
